Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 请
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:35.88,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1600)\pos(960,740)}小爱与大人的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节怎么过的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没什么 过得很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通…是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车 还会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明不白的真讨厌是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:00:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果停运的话可以去大哥哥家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 莫非你在想什么下流的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 电车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位乘客 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为降雪我们必须停止列车的运行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位乘客在列车恢复运行前稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？明明车站就在眼前了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 我的脸上有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.18,0:01:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不想在那天上班 工资会比平时高很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那天并不是和别的什么人一起度过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还暂时还像这样当个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都把我当大人看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这或许是对其一种反抗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会想确认一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大哥哥家里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位乘客久等了 列车即将恢复运行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次感谢各位乘客的支持和谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啦 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那话骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实前段时间爬上一阶…大人的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有察觉到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从几天起就不是小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的阶段是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…过个好年
